    "attributes": {
        "action": "Keep Care Leavers Digitally Connected",
        "additional_details": "Call to ensure care leavers are digitally connected \r\nWe are calling on government to:\r\n-\tExtend and improve uptake of the government scheme that provides digital devices  and internet for care leavers\r\n-\tEnsure every care leaver in England has a digital device and internet access for at least 12 months when they first live independently \r\n-\tRecommend that all local offers for care leavers include the right to a digital device and internet access",
        "background": "The digital divide between care leavers and the rest of society is growing. Care leavers are at risk of not being able to prosper in life due to the lack of support provided by their corporate parent to stay digitally connected when moving in to independent living.",
